title: Diaper Genie Bags Refills 270 (Pack of 3) Clean Laundry Scent | Diaper Pail Refills with Max Odor Lock | Holds up to 810 Newborn Diapers
description: Diaper Genie Clean Laundry Scent refill bags with Max Odor Lock feature upgraded and improved technology while offering the same trusted odor protection you know and love. Our Max Odor Lock™ refills consist of multiple layers to seal in dirty diaper odors while the built-in odor controlling antimicrobial inhibits bacteria growth on the film to help protect from germs. The Clean Laundry Scent helps neutralize strong diaper odors to keep your nursery smelling fresh and clean. Our continuous bags hold up to 270 newborn sized diapers so you can spend less time making trips to the trash and more time with your baby. When it’s emptying time, the opaque film hides the dirty diapers so you won’t have to relive all of those big blowouts - Phew! Since Clean Laundry Scent refills are made to fit Diaper Genie Complete and Expressions pails, you won’t ever have to rely on anything but the #1 selling diaper refill brand to keep your baby’s nursery smelling fresh and staying clean. Only Diaper Genie refills guarantee Odor Lock Protection. *Angelcare calculation based on Answers On Demand for the Diaper Refill Category for 52 weeks ending 09.10.2022 time period.
